These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, domino
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
House: ranch-style, victorian
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
2. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Game      | mah-jongg  | domino   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| House         | victorian | ranch-style |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, balloon-flower
House: townhouse, colonial
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the colonial house##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Flower           | balloon-flower         | aconite     |
| House     | townhouse   | colonial    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, techno
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, azure
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the fan of country is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Music-Genre    | techno     | country |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Color         | white         | azure        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

