.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-5::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: light-blue, green
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, engineer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, july
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
3. the engineer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Color      | light-blue | green       |
| Job           | engineer      | dancer     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery       | disaster   |
| Birthday           | july          | november |

