1. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the colombian is on the right of the argentine##1
3. the fan of indie is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Cigar   | havana   | davidoff  |
| Nationality   | argentine | colombian |
| Pet           | snake     | rat       |
| Music-Genre     | metal | indie       |

