.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, doctor
There 2 different types of food: kale, zucchini
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, satire
1. the doctor is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| Food         | kale          | zucchini     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation        | satire     |

 